=== 销量 ===
尽管本作收获了正面评价，但本作却是个商业败笔（虽然北美的销量尚可）<ref>{{cite web|last=Nadia|first=Oxford|date=June 24, 2007|title=Isle of Miscast Robots|url=http://www.1up.com/features/isle-miscast-robots?pager.offset=1|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117025942/http://www.1up.com/features/isle-miscast-robots?pager.offset=1|archive-date=November 17, 2015|access-date=July 15, 2021|work=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|page=2}}</ref>。稻船本打算着手开发更多洛克人系列的重制作品，迫于本作与另一部重制作品《[[洛克人洛克人|洛克人洛克人]]》的惨淡销量，计划不得不搁浅<ref name="1up2">{{cite web|last=Klepek|first=Patrick|date=May 16, 2006|title=Mega Man Creator Talks Future|url=http://www.1up.com/news/mega-man-creator-talks-future|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117025015/http://www.1up.com/news/mega-man-creator-talks-future|archive-date=November 17, 2015|access-date=July 15, 2021|work=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]}}</ref>。

后续本作于[[PlayStation_Store|PlayStation Store]]上线后重获成功，并于2014年4月成为[[PlayStation_Network|PlayStation Network]]第十佳畅销游戏。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|date=May 8, 2014|title=Best-selling PlayStation Network games of April revealed|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/best-selling-playstation-network-games-of-april-revealed/1100-6419514/|url-status=no|access-date=April 5, 2021|website=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archive-date=2022-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220205053049/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/best-selling-playstation-network-games-of-april-revealed/1100-6419514/}}</ref>

== 回响 ==
2011年卡普空宣布《洛克人洛克人》与《反乱猎人X》将会以二合一形式重新发售，同期以此形式发售的还有《[[怪物猎人携带版2nd|怪物猎人携带版2nd]]》及《[[怪物猎人携带版2nd_G|怪物猎人携带版2nd G]]》。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|last=Sahdev|first=Ishaan|date=October 17, 2011|title=Capcom And Gamestop Release MegaMan And Monster Hunter Dual Packs For PSP|url=https://www.siliconera.com/capcom-and-gamestop-release-megaman-and-monster-hunter-dual-packs-for-psp/|url-status=no|access-date=April 6, 2021|website=[[Siliconera|Siliconera]]|archive-date=2022-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220204190716/https://www.siliconera.com/capcom-and-gamestop-release-megaman-and-monster-hunter-dual-packs-for-psp/}}</ref>

2018年影片《西格玛之日》的高清重制版被包含在《洛克人X 周年纪念合集》及《洛克人X 周年纪念合集2》两部合集中，不过两部合集中并没有收录本作的游戏，同样没有被收录的3D游戏还有《[[洛克人X_指令任务|洛克人X 指令任务]]》。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Legarie|first=Destin|date=July 24, 2018|title=Mega Man X Legacy Collection 1 Review|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2018/07/24/mega-man-x-legacy-collection-1-review|url-status=no|access-date=April 5, 2021|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|archive-date=2022-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220407221713/https://www.ign.com/articles/2018/07/24/mega-man-x-legacy-collection-1-review}}</ref>

